{{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}
# /ui-review — Revisao de UI/UX

## Uso
```
/ui-review [alvo]
```

## Checklist de Revisao

### 1. Consistencia
- [ ] Cores do design system (tokens, nao hardcoded)
- [ ] Tipografia consistente (tamanhos, pesos, familias)
- [ ] Espacamento padronizado (scale do design system)
- [ ] Icones do mesmo conjunto
- [ ] Componentes do design system (nao custom sem necessidade)

### 2. Responsividade
- [ ] Mobile-first (funciona em 320px+)
- [ ] Breakpoints progressivos (sm, md, lg, xl)
- [ ] Layout adapta sem scroll horizontal
- [ ] Touch targets minimo 44x44px
- [ ] Textos legiveis em todos os tamanhos

### 3. Estados Visuais
| Estado | Obrigatorio |
|--------|------------|
| Default | Sim |
| Hover | Sim |
| Focus | Sim |
| Active | Sim |
| Disabled | Sim |
| Loading | Sim |
| Error | Sim |
| Empty | Sim |

### 4. Interatividade
- [ ] Hover com feedback visual
- [ ] Focus visivel em todos os elementos interativos
- [ ] Transicoes suaves (nao abruptas)
- [ ] Feedback de acao (loading, success, error)

### 5. Hierarquia Visual
- [ ] Elementos importantes em destaque
- [ ] Fluxo de leitura logico
- [ ] CTA (Call-to-Action) visivel
- [ ] Agrupamento logico de informacoes

### 6. Acessibilidade Basica
- [ ] Contraste minimo AA (4.5:1 texto normal, 3:1 texto grande)
- [ ] Labels em todos os inputs
- [ ] Alt text em imagens
- [ ] Navegacao por teclado funcional
- [ ] Hierarquia de headings (h1 → h2 → h3)

## Formato de Saida

```markdown
# UI Review — {alvo}

## Issues
### Criticas
1. {descricao} — {arquivo}:{linha}

### Importantes
1. {descricao}

### Sugestoes
1. {descricao}

## Score: X/10
```
{{else}}
# /ui-review — UI/UX Review

## Usage
```
/ui-review [target]
```

## Review Checklist

### 1. Consistency
- [ ] Design system colors (tokens, not hardcoded)
- [ ] Consistent typography (sizes, weights, families)
- [ ] Standardized spacing (design system scale)
- [ ] Icons from same set
- [ ] Design system components (no unnecessary custom)

### 2. Responsiveness
- [ ] Mobile-first (works at 320px+)
- [ ] Progressive breakpoints (sm, md, lg, xl)
- [ ] Layout adapts without horizontal scroll
- [ ] Touch targets minimum 44x44px
- [ ] Text readable at all sizes

### 3. Visual States
| State | Required |
|-------|----------|
| Default | Yes |
| Hover | Yes |
| Focus | Yes |
| Active | Yes |
| Disabled | Yes |
| Loading | Yes |
| Error | Yes |
| Empty | Yes |

### 4. Interactivity
- [ ] Hover with visual feedback
- [ ] Visible focus on all interactive elements
- [ ] Smooth transitions (not abrupt)
- [ ] Action feedback (loading, success, error)

### 5. Visual Hierarchy
- [ ] Important elements highlighted
- [ ] Logical reading flow
- [ ] CTA (Call-to-Action) visible
- [ ] Logical information grouping

### 6. Basic Accessibility
- [ ] Minimum AA contrast (4.5:1 normal text, 3:1 large text)
- [ ] Labels on all inputs
- [ ] Alt text on images
- [ ] Functional keyboard navigation
- [ ] Heading hierarchy (h1 → h2 → h3)

## Output Format

```markdown
# UI Review — {target}

## Issues
### Critical
1. {description} — {file}:{line}

### Important
1. {description}

### Suggestions
1. {description}

## Score: X/10
```
